OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780240300
OL,3,CElectricity prices set to rise by up
OL,4,Cto 7% from July
OL,6,FGuernsey Electricity will hike prices
OL,7,Fby a maximum of 7% from July 1st.
OL,9,FThe island's electricity company says
OL,10,Fthat while they know any increase in
OL,11,Fhousehold bills puts extra strain on
OL,12,Fislanders, more investment is needed
OL,13,Finto upgrading their infrastructure as
OL,14,Fthey expect increased demand.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
