CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780240300
OL,3,CElectricity prices set to rise by up
OL,4,Cto 7% from July
OL,6,FGuernsey Electricity say they already
OL,7,Fspend around #12 million a year on
OL,8,Freplacing existing equipment as it
OL,9,Freaches end of life. However, they say
OL,10,Fthey need to spend more money in
OL,11,Fupgrading electricity infrastructure
OL,12,Fto prepare for the future and expected
OL,13,Fincreased demand.
OL,15,FFor the typical customer with electric
OL,16,Fheating, their bill will increase by
OL,17,Faround #3 per week.
OL,19,FFor ones without electric heating, the
OL,20,Fbill will increase by around #1.55 per
OL,21,Fweek.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
