OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780240300
OL,3,CElectricity prices set to rise by up
OL,4,Cto 7% from July
OL,6,FThe standing charge will also increase
OL,7,Fby 3%- A lower than inflation rise and
OL,8,Fworks out at around 3 pence extra a
OL,9,Fday on a bill (under #10.50 a year).
OL,11,FIt's the latest in a string of annual
OL,12,Fprice hikes:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
