OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780240300
OL,3,CElectricity prices set to rise by up
OL,4,Cto 7% from July
OL,6,FAlan Bates, CEO of Guernsey
OL,7,FElectricity said: "I think we've seen
OL,8,Fthe impact of ten years of no tariff
OL,9,Fincreases. There is an element of
OL,10,Fcatch up, combined with obviously the
OL,11,FUkraine war, which pushed up inflation
OL,12,Flevels and interest rates, and also
OL,13,Fthe cost of buying equipment for the
OL,14,Fpower station and the network."
OL,16,FHe added: "This has made a perfect
OL,17,Fstorm of increases over the last five
OL,18,For six years."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/4
